T10TD4164E:169a-1: sh'i la pa ri ka th'a /
T10TD4164E:169a-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T10TD4164E:169a-5: rgya mtsho dang ni glang rjes kyi //
T10TD4164E:169a-6: khyad par dag ni gang yin pa //
T10TD4164E:169a-7: sbyin pa dang ni tshul khrims kyi //
T10TD4164E:169a-8: khyad par dag ni de yin no //
T10TD4164E:169a-9: gang zhig dad pa'i sems kyis ni //
T10TD4164E:169a-10: lo brgyar sbyin pa byin pa bas //
T10TD4164E:169a-11: gang zhig nyin gcig tshul khrims ni //
T10TD4164E:169a-12: bsrung ba de las khyad par 'phags //
T10TD4164E:169a-13: sbyin ba shan pa rnams dang ni //
T10TD4164E:169a-14: rigs ngan dag kyang sbyin par byed //
T10TD4164E:169a-15: gang yang rung bas tshul khrims ni //
T10TD4164E:169a-16: yongs su bsrung bar mi nus so //
T10TD4164E:169a-17: sbyin pa rab tu 'byor gyur kyang //
T10TD4164E:169a-18: de ni sbyin bdag chen po min //
T10TD4164E:169a-19: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa yis //
T10TD4164E:169a-20: sbyin bdag chen po yin par bshad //
T10TD4164E:169a-21: mgo bregs pa 'am gtsug phud ldan par rgyu //
T10TD4164E:169a-22: tshul khrims chu yis ral pa khyab par 'chang //
T10TD4164E:169a-23: cha lugs sna tshogs dag gis spyod gyur kyang //
T10TD4164E:169a-24: gal te tshul khrims med na rgyu spyod yin //
T10TD4164E:169a-25: gangg'a bgrod ba chu bon dar song ba 'am ;
T10TD4164E:169a-26: / dbyangs can chu 'am rdzing bur song ba 'am //
T10TD4164E:169a-27: ne le shar ni sten par byed pa yang //
T10TD4164E:169a-28: gal te tshul khrims kyis rgud la don med //
T10TD4164E:169a-29: ji ltar tshul khrims bla med ldan pa'i dri //
T10TD4164E:169a-30: dam pa mtho ris 'di na mi zad ldan //
T10TD4164E:169a-31: de ltar phreng ba'i dri ni khyab min cing //
T10TD4164E:169a-32: de bzhin byug pa'i dri yang 'byung mi 'gyur ;
T10TD4164E:169a-33: /'di na bdag dga' gzhan du 'gro ba bde //
T10TD4164E:169a-34: grags dang dga' zhing kun gyis bkur ba ste //
T10TD4164E:169a-35: chos ldan 'bras bu de de mang po mthong //
T10TD4164E:169a-36: tshul khrims 'bras bu drang srong chen pos gsungs //
T10TD4164E:169a-37: tshul khrims nad la sman pa'i mchog yin zhing //
T10TD4164E:169a-38: mun pa'i sgron ma nyam thag la skyabs dang //
T10TD4164E:169a-39: 'jigs la srungs dang phongs la nye du dang //
T10TD4164E:169a-40: 'chi ba'i rgya mtsho mtha' med gzings gyur yin //
T10TD4164E:169a-41: gang zhig 'dul ba'i tshul khrims rnam 'jig tshe //
T10TD4164E:169a-42: skrag zhugs tshul khrims ldan pa yod ma yin //
T10TD4164E:169a-43: de bas 'jig rten gzhan mtha' rgal sems kyis //
T10TD4164E:169b-0: gang zhig 'gro @169b 'dod des ni tshul khrims srungs //
T10TD4164E:169b-1: tshul khrims dri med ma lus ji bzhin gzhag //
T10TD4164E:169b-2: shes rab zhi bas yid ni yongs smin 'gyur //
T10TD4164E:169b-3: de bas rga shi nad 'jigs rnam thar pa //
T10TD4164E:169b-4: gang zhig thob 'dod des ni tshul khrims srungs //
T10TD4164E:169b-5: tshul khrims kyi gtam slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T10TD4164E:169b-7: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dza randha na dang /
T10TD4164E:169b-8: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba rin chen bzang pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
